Super quick tip I use all the time but people may not be aware - @github maintains a list of gitignores (with 161k ⭐️!) for every single language and you can clone them into your project with a oneliner:

npx gitignore &lt;language&gt;

just in case someone here doesnt know, now you do https://t.co/BTzUAO0ZSy

Little progressively enhanced CSS border reveal button using mask &amp;&amp; @​property

.border-button:hover { --complete: 100; }
.border-button::after {
  transition: --complete 0.4s;
  mask: conic-gradient(
    from var(--from),
    #000 var(--complete),
  );
} https://t.co/ikcx61Ntgw

